Titolo: Clockwork Knight

Anno: 1994

Descrizione: Clockwork Knight is a side-scrolling platform video game developed and published by Sega for the Sega Saturn. It was released in Japan in November 1994, in North America on the 1995 launch, and in Europe on July 8, 1995. Reviews were mixed, with critics praising the advanced graphics but criticizing the low difficulty, short length, and lack of gameplay innovation. It was followed by Clockwork Knight 2.